---

<!-- Hero About -->
<section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-700 to-emerald-900 text-white py-16 md:py-20">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1760159201329-521cd85a5bf9?ixlib=rb-4.1.0&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1470');"></div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/20 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6">
        Tentang Kami
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight">
        Partner Terpercaya Industri Pakan Ternak Indonesia
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-emerald-50 leading-relaxed">
        Sejak 2018, kami berkomitmen menyediakan bahan baku pakan ternak berkualitas tinggi langsung dari sumber tangan pertama untuk industri feedmill dan poultry shop di seluruh Indonesia.
      </p>
